{"tid":2457643,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"救命..夜晚周身痕但無明顯痕跡到底係發生乜事","createTime":"2021-03-22T21:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T12:38:03.000Z","uid":33905,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d84656668bb595cb8dffae6c33f89a19453b84ef","tid":2457643,"uid":33905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T21:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就死了 頂唔撚住了<br />\n每晚成身都會痕 你話好痕又唔係 合埋眼果下就開始黎料<br />\nR左呢個位就唔痕 會變成另一個位痕 望落完全無痕跡 最多有時有個位會起左粒紅點 R完5-10分鐘內就會消失<br />\n唔撚R就會好惡 會越來越痕 痕到好似俾針拮左一下咁 根本訓唔撚到 一定要R一下佢先會消 但一R左就會係第2個位開始痕 由頭到腳完全隨機 上至頭皮塊面 背隻 手手腳腳 春袋都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為乾燥試過茶CREAM 無用<br />\n手肘個接位以前間唔時都有濕疹 但唔嚴重 近呢兩年又跟本無番發過<br />\n有無巴打知究竟係咩事 或者有無人有過差唔多經歷<br />\n點先會好 救命呀 唔想晚晚就起勢RRR R完都訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa71f6b7c1fd3e4a72ae54cf7dcd135b6586c05a","tid":2457643,"uid":344625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T21:58:17.000Z","msg":"沖涼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e59b511a64c41796037f04d73f587bf9ad8c159","tid":2457643,"uid":359210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T22:23:35.000Z","msg":"睇醫生 可能係真菌感染 肉眼睇唔到"},{"pid":"003f11f3ff66b1460399b0c28dabc5ee7245c0e9","tid":2457643,"uid":33905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fa71f6b7c1fd3e4a72ae54cf7dcd135b6586c05a","tid":2457643,"uid":344625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T21:58:17.000Z","msg":"沖涼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:42:12.000Z","msg":"沖太多驚仲痕"},{"pid":"d7d5be92f0a4ebdfd1597e44be55c9b5774c1b26","tid":2457643,"uid":33905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e59b511a64c41796037f04d73f587bf9ad8c159","tid":2457643,"uid":359210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s